trail.by.title: trail.by
trail.by.text: Trail helps you discover the world of ecotourism in Belarus. We have collected a variety of eco-trails from all over Belarus so that everyone can find a route to their liking

pizza order bot.title: pizza order bot
pizza order bot.text: This bot's purpose is to make pizza order easier and faster. Though it has limited functionality it is still pretty good for some small orders. But... actions speak louder than words, try it!

seebelarus.by.title: seebelarus.by
seebelarus.by.text: My name is Tatyana Shkarubskaya. I’m a certified guide in Minsk. I’m keen on touring my native land myself, finding out different things about past and nowadays of Belarus.
